Raw Iron=Kruda Fero
Block of Raw Iron=Bloko de Kruda Fero
Raw Iron. Mine an Iron ore to get it.=Kruda Fero. Minu Feran ercon por akiri ĝin.
A block of raw Iron is mostly a decorative block but also useful as a compact storage of raw Iron.=
